Hand motion infiller — algorithm adapted from HaWoR

The Python files in this directory (`network.py`, `filling.py`,
`rotation.py`) are derived from the HaWoR motion infiller reference
implementation, with EgoInfinity-side adaptations described below.

Upstream:  https://github.com/ThunderVVV/HaWoR
Citation:  Zhang, J., et al. "HaWoR: World-Space Hand Motion
            Reconstruction from Egocentric Videos." CVPR 2025.

EgoInfinity adaptations:
- Self-contained re-pack of the infiller submodule (removes the
  unnecessary MANO dependency at infill time; uses our existing
  WiLoR-loaded MANO).
- File-level docstrings record which upstream file each module was
  derived from (see top of each .py).

Please consult the HaWoR repository for the upstream license terms.
If the upstream license file is not present here, treat this code as
"derived from HaWoR" and respect HaWoR's published terms.

The HaWoR infiller weight (infiller.pt) is downloaded from the upstream
HuggingFace repo (ThunderVVV/HaWoR) by scripts/setup_weights.sh into
${EGOINFINITY_CKPT_DIR}/infiller.pt; it is NOT redistributed by this repo.
